## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the relationship between dementia and social isolation. The findings are limited to the sources accessed, and there may be additional factors contributing to social isolation in dementia that are not covered here. Furthermore, the dynamic nature of dementia and its impact on individuals can vary widely, suggesting that personalized approaches to mitigating social isolation are necessary.

